snippet.title: Life in Bunker Review - Worthabuy?
snippet.description:
You've been elected as the new Bunker Warden! Now you must take control over a group of fellow bunker residents and try to make them last until the surface becomes habitable.  Review copy supplied by developer. (Thanks)
